  "detailed_description": "Defeat all enemies in 200 levels and upgrade your spaceship more and more!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPure action:<br />\r\nIn 200 levels you have to defeat all opponents.<br />\r\nIn a store you can upgrade your spaceship more and more.<br />\r\nPlay alone or simultaneously in pairs on one monitor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStore:<br />\r\nIn the game you can collect money and extras.<br />\r\nWith the money you can level up your spaceship in a store.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1- or 2-player mode:<br />\r\nAlone you can try to defeat your opponents in all 200 levels.<br />\r\nIf you play as a team of two, you and your teammate will also fight for money and extras.",
